NOTICE OF PROPRIETARY RIGHTS
=============================

The underlying algorithms, protocols, and technical implementations in this
repository — including but not limited to:

  - CAV (Calibrated Adversarial Verification) consensus protocol
  - CCB (Claude Code Best) multi-agent orchestration framework
  - PEV (Plan-Execute-Verify) hypothesis-driven execution loop
  - SharedLedger immutable reducer architecture
  - Cross-agent Propagator and Scheduler algorithms
  - VerdictEngine regex-based judgement system
  - Three-layer fault-tolerant parser pipeline
  - Canonical Test Plans table and ToolPlan schema
  - Hypothesis Bank typed state machine (8-kind taxonomy)
  - Stale cascade propagation algorithm
  - ∇H ≤ 0 fixed-point convergence detection

— are the exclusive intellectual property of the copyright holder.

